event.title: Google I/O Live Stream
event.description:
Many of us haven't been lucky enough to snag a ticket to Google I/O in San Francisco, luckily Somo have kindly offered to live stream the first two sessions for us instead!

Come join us for all of the latest reveals and news from Google along with some food and drink.

**Spaces are limited so please only RSVP if you're definitely going to attend.**

The keynote itself starts at 5:30pm but you're welcome to arrive from 5:00pm onwards. Full IO schedule.Â
